dding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'>가</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\"><span style='box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'>. </span></span><span style='box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'>장학생 선발 직후 기부자에게 감사편지 제출 필수</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\"><span style='box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'>, </span></span><span style='box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'>미제출 시 장학생 선발 취소</span></p>\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'>나</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\"><span style='box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'>. </span></span><span style='box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'>파견 취소 및 연기 시 장학 선발 취소</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\"><span style='box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'>, </span></span><span style='box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'>차순위자를 대상자로 선정</span></p>\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;'> </p>\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;'><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\"><span style='box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'>11. </span></span><span style='box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'>문의</span>: <span style='box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'>글로벌교류팀 </span><span sty